dct_title_s: Regional Consolidated Zoning Dane County, Wisconsin 2003
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents regional consolidated zoning for Racine, Wisconsin in 2003. The dataset was originally published by the Southeast Wisconsin Regional Planning Commission (SEWRPC) on January 23, 2004.
